casebody.data:
Kenneth S. WEST, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Mike CARROLL, Secretary, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3809 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

As it appears that the petitioner is represented by counsel in the proceeding in the trial court, the petition for writ of prohibition is dismissed. See Logan v. State, 846 So. 2d 472 (Fla. 2003).

KHOUZAM, MORRIS, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
